  "description": "<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Sada hajde da proverimo brojeve od 90 do 99.</p>\n<p>Na španski, broj 90 se zove <span class=\"highlighted-text\">noventa</span>.</p>\n<p>Ovi brojevi se formiraju korišćenjem reči trideset <span class=\"highlighted-text\">noventa</span> (90), praćen spojnikom <span class=\"highlighted-text\">y</span> (\"na\"), zatim brojem jedinica (1-9).</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\">Broj</th>\n<th align=\"left\">Kihispania</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">90</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Noventa</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">91</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Noventa y uno</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">92</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Noventa y dos</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">93</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Noventa y tres</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">94</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Noventa y cuatro</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">95</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Noventa y cinco</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">96</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Noventa y seis</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">97</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Noventa y siete</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">98</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Noventa y ocho</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">99</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Noventa y nueve</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>Broj <span class=\"highlighted-text\">noventa y uno</span> (91) je jedinstven u ovoj seriji jer se menja u <span class=\"highlighted-text\">noventa y un</span> pre muškog imena. Na primer:</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Noventa y un años</span> - Devedeset i jedna godina.</p>\n</section>",
